shows.name: Under the Dome
shows.summary: Under the Dome is the story of a small town that is suddenly and inexplicably sealed off from the rest of the world by an enormous transparent dome.

shows.name: Person of Interest
shows.summary: You are being watched. The government has a secret system, a machine that spies on you every hour of every day.

shows.name: Bitten
shows.summary: Based on the critically acclaimed series of novels from Kelley Armstrong. Set in Toronto and upper New York State, Bitten follows Elena Michaels, the world’s only female werewolf.

shows.name: Arrow
shows.summary: After a violent shipwreck, billionaire playboy Oliver Queen was missing and presumed dead for five years before returning with a mission to fight crime.

shows.name: True Detective
shows.summary: True Detective centers on troubled cops and the investigations that drive them to the edge, exploring themes of darkness and morality.

shows.name: The 100
shows.summary: Ninety-seven years after nuclear Armageddon decimated planet Earth, the only survivors are exiled humans living in space who send 100 juvenile prisoners back to test the planet.

shows.name: Homeland
shows.summary: Homeland follows a CIA officer who suspects that a prisoner of war has been turned by al-Qaeda and now poses a threat to the United States.

shows.name: Glee
shows.summary: A musical comedy about a group of ambitious young adults in search of strength, acceptance, and their place in the world, set in a high school glee club.

shows.name: Revenge
shows.summary: Revenge is not a story about forgiveness; it’s a show about retribution as Emily Thorne infiltrates the Hamptons elite to take down those who wronged her family.

shows.name: Grimm
shows.summary: A homicide detective discovers he is a Grimm, a guardian who must keep the balance between humanity and mythological creatures.

shows.name: Gotham
shows.summary: A prequel to the Batman saga, Gotham explores the origins of Commissioner Gordon and the villains who shaped the city’s dark legacy.

shows.name: Lost Girl
shows.summary: Lost Girl follows supernatural seductress Bo, a Succubus who feeds on the sexual energy of humans, as she navigates the fae world and her mysterious origins.
